<p>Women Who Code supports equality and inclusion in the tech industry on a global scale through resources, tools, training, and networking. Your support allows us to amplify this movement to promote, inspire, and advance more diverse women leaders, contributors, and change-makers in tech.</p>

<p>Your donation will go to programs supporting our global community. This helps Women Who Code efficiently run our growing organization, produce innovative programming, and expand our reach to ensure that more women everywhere have the opportunity to pursue and excel in technology careers.</p>

<p>We encourage you to keep growing with Women Who Code through membership, volunteerism, and events! We are glad you have chosen to join us on this journey, and we can't wait to see what the future holds!</p>

